com.exacttarget.etpushsdk

Class ETSendDataReceiver

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.BroadcastReceiver
      • android.support.v4.content.WakefulBroadcastReceiver
        • com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.ETSendDataReceiver

  • public class ETSendDataReceiver
extends WakefulBroadcastReceiver
    BroadcastReceiver to handle sending data to ExactTarget. You must include this as a <receiver> in your AndroidManifest.xml. 
     
 <manifest ...>
   ...
   <application ...>
     ...
     <!-- ET Broadcast Receivers for for sending data (required) -->
     <receiver android:name="com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.ETSendDataReceiver"/>
     ...
   </application>
   ...
 </manifest>
